  "text": "Fine mapping of chromosome 5p15.33 in Han Chinese of two measurements was used in the statistical analyses. [CITATION_1] The CV of the two measurements was 0.38% and 0.29% for the telomere reaction and the single-copy gene reaction, respectively. Technicians were blinded to the case-control status. RTL was calculated according to Cawthon's formula, 2 2(DCt1-DCt2) 5 2 2DDCt . The inter-plate variation of the quality control samples for RTL measurement was 10.16% and the intraplate variation was 8.69%.",
